title: Steve Wilkos Prostitute Town Meeting
description:
***********************************************************************************    
    PROSTITUTE TOWN MEETING:
    ------------------------
    Steve goes on the road to Detroit and interviews 9 different prostitutes in jail. They tell different stories about their lives, and how they went down the wrong path. We also take a look at some of their arrest footage, and discuss a program that the Wayne Co Sheriff's office is doing to help some of the inmates get their lives back on track. 

ENJOY PLEASE SEED AND SAY THANK YOU
